title: Affordable living! Wonderful floor plans for every budget!
posting_body: ['The Duxbury Apartments is in the heart of Tacoma.', 'With wonderful views, parks and museums within walking distance.', 'Its near local shops and fine dining.', 'For more information or to schedule a tour, please call our office:', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 9am-5pm', 'Saturday-Sunday: CLOSED', 'You can apply online at: <URL>', 'Apartment Home Features:', '*Spacious Floor Plans', '*Refrigerator', '*Stove', '*Spacious Closet', '*Built in Storages', 'Amenities:', '*Easy access to I-5 & I-90', '*Pet Friendly.', '*Beautiful Scenic Views of Puget Sound.', '*Secured Entry', '*On-site Laundry', 'QUALIFICATIONS:', '**Must have 2.85 times rent in gross monthly income', '**Must have NO evictions in past 7 years', '**Must NOT owe any money to any apartments/rental companies', '**Must NOT have an open bankruptcy', '**Collections/past due balances must not be over $3,000(excluding medical/student loans)', 'Visit our website for this and many other great properties at: <URL>/', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
